00:02:28.687 --> 00:02:31.887
What, Your Highness? Are you jealous?

00:02:33.247 --> 00:02:37.487
Or are you regretting why you
slaughtered the Shen that night?

00:02:37.488 --> 00:02:38.287
You!

00:02:42.008 --> 00:02:43.287
