00:02:47.488 --> 00:02:49.967
I didn't see you showing mercy then.

00:02:52.728 --> 00:02:53.847
All those years,

00:02:54.847 --> 00:02:56.447
we walked side by side,

00:02:57.488 --> 00:02:58.927
through life and death,

00:02:58.928 --> 00:02:59.727
sharing hardship.

00:02:59.728 --> 00:03:03.608
And yet you refuse
to trust me even a little?

00:03:04.768 --> 00:03:05.806
The killer left behind

00:03:05.807 --> 00:03:08.407
a token of the Mobei royal family.

00:03:09.087 --> 00:03:10.328
My mother,

00:03:11.048 --> 00:03:13.208
my brother, my sister

00:03:13.487 --> 00:03:15.367
all were slain by a soft sword.

00:03:16.087 --> 00:03:17.368
Tell me,

00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:22.048
who else in the Mobei royal family
uses a soft sword?

00:03:22.168 --> 00:03:23.167
Me.

00:03:23.687 --> 00:03:25.567
So how can I trust you?

00:03:26.175 --> 00:03:27.687
Give me some time.

00:03:28.567 --> 00:03:30.447
I will find the true culprit

00:03:30.448 --> 00:03:31.447
