years fighting on the border,

00:04:58.567 --> 00:05:00.087
were to see this,

00:05:00.212 --> 00:05:02.007
would he raise his sword against you?

00:05:02.648 --> 00:05:03.870
Yuwen Que,

00:05:04.528 --> 00:05:05.887
